\c 4  
\s1 The Work Ridiculed  
\m
\v 1 \w Now|strong="H1961"\w* \w when|strong="H3588"\w* \w Sanballat|strong="H5571"\w* \w heard|strong="H8085"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w were|strong="H1961"\w* rebuilding \w the|strong="H8085"\w* \w wall|strong="H2346"\w*, \w he|strong="H3588"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w furious|strong="H2734"\w* \w and|strong="H3389"\w* filled \w with|strong="H3389"\w* indignation. \w He|strong="H3588"\w* ridiculed \w the|strong="H8085"\w* Jews  
\v 2 before \w his|strong="H3605"\w* associates \w and|strong="H3389"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w army|strong="H3389"\w* \w of|strong="H3605"\w* Samaria, saying, “\w What|strong="H6213"\w* \w are|strong="H6213"\w* \w these|strong="H6213"\w* feeble Jews \w doing|strong="H6213"\w*? \w Can|strong="H6213"\w* \w they|strong="H6213"\w* restore \w the|strong="H3605"\w* wall \w by|strong="H6213"\w* \w themselves|strong="H6213"\w*?\f + \fr 4:2 \ft Or Will they commit themselves to God?\f* \w Will|strong="H3389"\w* \w they|strong="H6213"\w* \w offer|strong="H6213"\w* sacrifices? \w Will|strong="H3389"\w* \w they|strong="H6213"\w* \w complete|strong="H3605"\w* \w it|strong="H6213"\w* \w in|strong="H6213"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* day? \w Can|strong="H6213"\w* \w they|strong="H6213"\w* \w bring|strong="H6213"\w* \w these|strong="H6213"\w* \w burnt|strong="H6213"\w* stones back \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w life|strong="H3605"\w* \w from|strong="H3389"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* mounds \w of|strong="H3605"\w* rubble?”   
