\c 5  
\s1 Nehemiah Defends the Oppressed  
\m
\v 1 \w About|strong="H1961"\w* \w that|strong="H5971"\w* \w time|strong="H1961"\w* \w there|strong="H1961"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w great|strong="H1419"\w* \w outcry|strong="H6818"\w* \w from|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H1961"\w* \w people|strong="H5971"\w* \w and|strong="H1419"\w* \w their|strong="H1961"\w* wives against \w their|strong="H1961"\w* fellow \w Jews|strong="H3064"\w*.   
