\pmo “\w It|strong="H5921"\w* \w is|strong="H1697"\w* \w reported|strong="H8085"\w* \w among|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w nations|strong="H1471"\w*—\w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w Geshem|strong="H1654"\w* \f + \fr 6:6 \ft Hebrew Gashmu, a variant of Geshem; see verse 1.\f* agrees—\w that|strong="H8085"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w Jews|strong="H3064"\w* \w are|strong="H1471"\w* plotting \w to|strong="H5921"\w* revolt, \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w this|strong="H3651"\w* \w is|strong="H1697"\w* \w why|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \w are|strong="H1471"\w* \w building|strong="H1129"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w wall|strong="H2346"\w*. \w According|strong="H5921"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w these|strong="H8085"\w* \w reports|strong="H1697"\w*, \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \w are|strong="H1471"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* become \w their|strong="H8085"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w*,  
